<h2>EXECUTIVE SUMMARY</h2>
<br>
<p>
Jepp Davis Consult, LLP is a boutique management consulting firm that specialises in providing innovative business solutions for small businesses and is located in Accra, Greater Accra Region, the heart of Ghana’s capital. The firm provides financial advice and financial management, business advisory services to highly esteemed clients.
<br>
<br>
Our services cover areas such as; Financial services consulting, Accounting solutions, Mergers and Acquisitions, Finance modelling, Business valuation and other business-related services.
<br>
<br>
Being aware of the presence of the top giants in management consulting, and the preponderance of small businesses juxtaposed with the numerous challenges they face which are mostly finance related, we have strategically positioned our firm to meet this demand by providing bespoke financial solutions to Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises (MSMEs).
<br>
<br>
Our foundation is built on hard-work focused on achieving goals by meeting the needs of our clients with enthusiasm, knowledge and integrity. We aim to do this at very affordable rates that would not put holes in the pockets of our clients.
<br>
<br>
At Jepp Davis, we ensure a partnership with highly knowledgeable financial advisors who combine sound professional ethics, values and a wealth of experience to provide a wide variety of financial services to achieve sustainable business results and positive social and environmental outcomes all delivered through proven tools and methodologies.
<br>
<br>
Jepp Davis is founded by Elikplimi K. Agbloyor (PhD, ACCA). The firm will be managed by the partners as together, they provide extensive knowledge in business consulting.
</p>
