<h3>Company Description</h3>
<p>
<br>
Jepp Davis is an innovative business solutions provider working with SMEs across all sectors in Ghana. We help clients generate sustainable business results and positive social and environmental outcomes all delivered through proven tools and methodologies.
Our focus is to give full financial advisory services to small and medium enterprises developing strategies to get the most value from deals.
<br>
<br>
Jepp Davis is a limited partnership company that can be located at Impact Hub in Accra, Ghana. The company may be contacted by phone: +233(0)268818105, or +233(0)505624969, or web: www.jeppdavis.com or email: info@jeppdavis.com.
Vision Statement
<br>
<br>
Our vision is to create a global consulting firm inspired by entrepreneurship and a unique culture and also to achieve our goals by meeting the needs of our clients with enthusiasm, knowledge and integrity.
Mission Statement
<br>
<br>
Our mission is to provide value-adding and innovative financial solutions tailored to the needs of SMEs in emerging and developing markets. Also, to provide unparalleled professional and trusted financial advisory services that assist individuals and businesses in operating sustainably.
<br>
<br>
Value Proposition
Enterprises no more enjoy longer life span in operation. This is majorly due to the poor financial decisions made by entrepreneurs who have little understanding about how to solve the challenges faced in their businesses. Jepp Davis exists to provide bespoke business solutions to these businesses to ensure they achieve the best business results.
</p>
